_sText: This is my first attempt at using HDR lighting in my maps. I did compile the cubemaps correctly so there should be no problems with that. I was inspired to create this map after playing on the map awpf_crumblecup. I liked the quickness of the rounds but it still had some tactics involved. The maximum player slots is 36. I recommend playing with 10 or less players total though. If you are going to host this map on your server, then give me the IP and I will definitely come and play on it. Feel free to decompile the map if you really need to for some reason. Don't distribute to other sites though unless I give you the go-ahead. Please assess and give some Constructive Criticism.
